Syntax: help
Syntax: help <topic>
Syntax: help index

<h>'s online help files are carefully maintained and cross-referenced
for ease of use.  Additionally, it has been indexed so that similar topics
can be found easily.

The top of the index can be seen by typing 'help' and will list the major
sub-indexes.  The sub-indexes should list all available help topics in that
category.

If you remain confused about anything, it may be worthwhile to find a FAQ and
read it as it goes into more depth on esoteric subjects.

Related Topics: GENERAL INFO
